Zotonic mod_akismet
===================

Akismet comment spam filtering for Zotonic. 
Implements a simple comment spam defense with Akismet.


How to use mod_akismet
----------------------

Zotonic 0.7 and higher

  1. zotonic installmodule mod_akismet
  2. Sign-up for an Akismet.com API key at https://akismet.com/signup/
  3. In the "config" section in the Zotonic admin, create a config key:
     mod_akismet/akismet_key - Your Akismet.com API key
  4. Now, activate both the Zotonic Comments and Akismet modules 
     under "Modules".  


Zotonic <= 0.6

  1. cd $ZOTONIC_HOME/modules
  2. git clone git://github.com/secYOUre/mod_akismet.git mod_akismet
  3. Sign-up for an Akismet.com API key at https://akismet.com/signup/
  4. In the "config" section in the Zotonic admin, create a config key:
     mod_akismet/akismet_key - Your Akismet.com API key
  5. Now, activate both the Zotonic Comments and Akismet modules 
     under "Modules".  
